title: Latvia Food Inflation
description: Cost of food in Latvia increased 29.50 percent in October of 2022 over the same month in the previous year. Food Inflation in Latvia averaged 4.45 percent from 1998 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 29.50 percent in October of 2022 and a record low of -7.80 percent in January of 2010. This page provides - Latvia Food Inflation - actual values, historical data, forecast, chart, statistics, economic calendar and news.
author: Central Statistical Bureau of Latvia
